title: LeBron, Cavaliers start season with same expectations
text: > Ohio LeBron, Cavaliers start season with same expectations This Monday, Oct. 12, 2015, photo shows Cleveland Cavaliers' LeBron James during an NBA basketball game against the Memphis Grizzlies in Columbus, Ohio. No player carries the burden of expectations like James, still the league's best all-around player and most indomitable force entering his 13th season. No player is asked to do as much year after year as James, who has played in five consecutive NBA Finals and will likely extend his streak to six _ assuming, that is, the Cavs get healthy and can stay healthy. (AP Photo/Jay LaPrete)
